    <item>
      <title>力拓铁矿石产量上升，铜产量预期令人失望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/rio-tinto-iron-ore-shipments-rise-despite-china-demand-softening</link>
      <description><![CDATA[力拓集团表示，尽管 5 月份铁路中断和中国需求低迷，但第二季度西澳大利亚铁矿石出货量仍小幅增加，但警告称，全年铜产量将处于其预期范围的低端。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/rio-tinto-iron-ore-shipments-rise-despite-china-demand-softening</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 22:38:00 GMT</pubDate>
